419
00:24:25,150 --> 00:24:26,780
What's going on with these two today?

420
00:24:27,350 --> 00:24:28,780
They're acting like robots.

421
00:24:29,500 --> 00:24:30,350
I have no idea.

422
00:24:30,940 --> 00:24:32,910
