438
00:25:24,110 --> 00:25:25,220
Let's just have fun.

439
00:25:25,390 --> 00:25:26,110
Am I right?

440
00:25:27,220 --> 00:25:29,020
Yes, of course.

441
00:25:30,540 --> 00:25:32,110
I think this kind of peace and quiet

442
00:25:32,740 --> 00:25:33,870
