553
00:32:29,460 --> 00:32:30,870
My memories of my family

554
00:32:32,940 --> 00:32:33,980
are painful.

555
00:32:37,630 --> 00:32:39,830
So when you proposed to me,

556
00:32:40,940 --> 00:32:42,070
